# Key Configuration Files

-   **`package.json`**: Defines project dependencies and scripts ([package.json](mdc:package.json)).
-   **`vite.config.ts`**: Configuration for the Vite build tool ([vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts)).
-   **`tsconfig.json`**: Base TypeScript compiler options ([tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)).
-   **`tailwind.config.js`**: Tailwind CSS configuration ([tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js)).
-   **`postcss.config.js`**: PostCSS configuration ([postcss.config.js](mdc:postcss.config.js)).
-   **`eslint.config.js`**: ESLint configuration for code linting ([eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js)).
-   **`index.html`**: The main HTML entry point for the application ([index.html](mdc:index.html)).
